summary: Multi-currency underpayment across EUR, AUD, USD, and NOK Card streams from February through May 2025. Contract rate is 3.8% but reconciliation shows effective rates of 3.50-3.60%. Total underpayment: 74,226.71 EUR. EUR Card accounts for the majority (64,140.91 EUR).

notes.text: Effective rates consistently ~3.5% across all currencies, well below the 3.8% contract rate. Gap of ~0.3 percentage points sustained over 4 months.
January 2025 shows correct 3.8% rate for EUR and AUD. The discrepancy begins in February 2025.
EUR daily data shows day-level breakdown. AUD, USD, NOK data available at monthly granularity only.
